Class Description
Actor
An abstract class for all the actors that can be present in the game world, such as: Animal, Logs, Obstacles etc.
ActorControllers
An interface for the different controllers.
ActorMovement
The movement controls of Actor objects are written in this class.
Animal
Animal class that extends the Actor class.
AnimalController
A controller class for the Animal model following the MVC pattern.

Test for the AnimalController class.
AnimalTest
Test for the Animal class.

This class is responsible for what happens at the end of the game.
